when he has nothing?

282
00:18:19,314 --> 00:18:22,715
Kim Myung Ha.
I'm telling you right now.

283
00:18:22,715 --> 00:18:25,284
If you don't have what you need,
don't even think about marriage.

284
00:18:27,455 --> 00:18:28,655
Don't worry.

285
00:18:28,655 --> 00:18:31,794
