286
00:18:42,705 --> 00:18:43,734
Sure.

287
00:18:45,334 --> 00:18:47,345
Don't date a woman like me.

288
00:18:49,105 --> 00:18:50,115
Please.

289
00:19:02,625 --> 00:19:03,695
