how the world works.

298
00:19:33,484 --> 00:19:35,224
That's how he gets to learn.

299
00:19:37,355 --> 00:19:40,465
Young Ha. Just stick to your path.

300
00:19:40,895 --> 00:19:42,395
Don't look back.

301
00:19:43,734 --> 00:19:46,034
That will also help him.

302
00:19:54,345 --> 00:19:55,945
Should I go to the food stall
with you?

303
00:19:57,375 --> 00:19:58,645
Just go home.

304
00:19:59,744 --> 00:20:00,945
Okay.

305
00:20:05,115 --> 00:20:06,355
Myung Ha's here.

306
00:20:12,125 --> 00:20:14,324
How's your Chinese friend doing?

307
00:20:16,764 --> 00:20:19,734
Yes. Let's talk later.

308
00:20:20,365 --> 00:20:21,465
Sure.

309
00:20:22,804 --> 00:20:24,004
Let's go.

310
00:20:25,205 --> 00:20:26,405
Bye.

311
00:20:34,715 --> 00:20:36,415
What are you doing? What?

312
00:20:37,014 --> 00:20:38,215
Sit down for a sec.

313
00:20:44,395 --> 00:20:47,665
I met Gwang Jae today.

314
00:20:49,294 --> 00:20:51,965
Gwang Jae? Where?

315
00:20:52,465 --> 00:20:53,705
At my school.

316
00:20:54,635 --> 00:20:56,034
What was he doing there?

317
00:20:57,875 --> 00:21:01,375
He was selling used clothes
to my friend.

318
00:21:02,705 --> 00:21:03,744
What?

319
