320
00:21:08,014 --> 00:21:09,314
He seemed struggling.

321
00:21:10,484 --> 00:21:11,685
But...

322
00:21:12,455 --> 00:21:14,185
did you really break up with him?

323
00:21:17,054 --> 00:21:18,754
I know Kyung Ha would do that,

324
00:21:19,595 --> 00:21:21,524
but I didn't know about you.

325
00:21:23,465 --> 00:21:24,994
That's what Gwang Jae wanted.

326
00:21:24,994 --> 00:21:26,665
You really think he meant it?

327
00:21:27,334 --> 00:21:28,935
He meant it.

328
00:21:29,534 --> 00:21:31,435
But why is he selling clothes?

329
00:21:31,534 --> 00:21:33,574
He told me he was going abroad.

330
00:21:44,915 --> 00:21:46,014
It's...

331
00:21:46,484 --> 00:21:49,084
Gwang Jae's bike jacket.

332
00:21:49,425 --> 00:21:52,224
There are probably things
he couldn't tell you.

333
00:21:52,224 --> 00:21:53,425
You should find out.

334
00:22:05,935 --> 00:22:07,845
