336
00:22:11,514 --> 00:22:12,814
Will you do it for me?

337
00:22:24,195 --> 00:22:25,895
It's for quick sale.

338
00:22:25,895 --> 00:22:27,925
The owner asked me to sell it quick.

339
00:22:27,925 --> 00:22:30,794
2 million is a very cheap price.

340
00:22:30,794 --> 00:22:32,665
The site itself is huge.

341
00:22:32,935 --> 00:22:34,234
- Ma'am.
- My goodness.

342
00:22:34,234 --> 00:22:35,935
Hello.

343
00:22:37,334 --> 00:22:39,334
- Is this house on sale?
- I guess so.

344
00:22:40,244 --> 00:22:41,445
My goodness, Gwang Jae.

345
00:22:41,544 --> 00:22:45,375
Tell him to take
the rest of his belongings.

346
00:22:45,375 --> 00:22:47,145
He's abroad.

347
00:22:47,345 --> 00:22:48,945
He stopped by a few days ago.

348
00:22:48,945 --> 00:22:50,415
A few days ago...

349
00:22:50,955 --> 00:22:51,955
What?

350
00:22:52,655 --> 00:22:55,284
- Uncle Hyo Dong!
- Gwang Jae!

351
00:22:55,324 --> 00:22:57,355
Gwang Jae! Gwang Jae!

352
00:22:58,324 --> 00:23:01,465
- Uncle Hyo Dong!
- Gwang Jae!

353
00:23:03,695 --> 00:23:06,705
I'm so glad to see you.
How have you been?

354
00:23:06,705 --> 00:23:08,665
I thought you went abroad.

355
00:23:08,665 --> 00:23:11,774
What are you talking about?

356
00:23:12,504 --> 00:23:14,105
Where did you stay?

357
00:23:14,405 --> 00:23:16,715
- By riverside.
- My goodness.

358
00:23:17,744 --> 00:23:19,175
The house is on the market?

359
00:23:19,845 --> 00:23:20,984
My house?

360
00:23:21,345 --> 00:23:23,054
It's for quick sale.

361
00:23:24,054 --> 00:23:27,054
It looks like they're going to sell
everything and take off.

362
00:23:32,324 --> 00:23:33,465
Gwang Jae.

363
00:23:34,195 --> 00:23:35,564
Actually...

364
00:23:38,395 --> 00:23:39,804
there's something I have confess.

365
00:23:44,474 --> 00:23:45,504
I...

366
00:23:48,244 --> 00:23:50,615
was deceived by CEO Nam.

367
00:23:55,744 --> 00:23:58,655
I deserve to die.

368
00:23:58,915 --> 00:24:00,284
I deserve to die.

369
00:24:01,054 --> 00:24:03,395
What are you talking about?
Be clear.

370
00:24:03,824 --> 00:24:05,095
Stop crying.

371
00:24:05,095 --> 00:24:08,595
I was deceived. I was deceived.

372
00:24:10,395 --> 00:24:11,895
I was deceived twice.

373
00:24:12,595 --> 00:24:14,064
At first, I didn't know
that he fooled me.

374
00:24:14,304 --> 00:24:16,165
And the second time,
I had no choice.

375
00:24:17,205 --> 00:24:19,945
I was deceived by CEO Nam twice.

376
00:24:22,274 --> 00:24:24,115
I'm such an idiot.

377
00:24:26,345 --> 00:24:28,814
I made Gye Dong die.

378
00:24:33,484 --> 00:24:36,754
I'm sorry, Gwang Jae. I'm sorry.

379
00:24:38,994 --> 00:24:40,895
Because of gambling debts,

380
00:24:41,365 --> 00:24:43,435
I ended up laying my hands on
the company fund.

381
00:24:43,935 --> 00:24:45,064
What?

382
00:24:45,365 --> 00:24:47,705
I needed money as the debt grew.

383
00:24:50,205 --> 00:24:54,105
CEO Nam and Tae Il knew
and put a bait.

384
00:24:55,645 --> 00:24:58,314
I handed over
Gye Dong's recipe book...

385
00:24:58,915 --> 00:25:01,415
to private moneylenders
instead of money.

386
00:25:04,415 --> 00:25:07,024
I thought I'd get it back soon.

387
00:25:08,724 --> 00:25:12,355
Then the recipe plagiarism incident
broke out.

388
00:25:13,925 --> 00:25:17,135
The recipe book in the main office
disappeared too.

389
00:25:19,234 --> 00:25:22,605
Actually the manager said
CEO Nam did something...

390
00:25:22,905 --> 00:25:24,474
suspicious in the kitchen that day.

391
00:25:25,504 --> 00:25:28,004
I think CEO Nam and Tae Il are...

392
00:25:28,244 --> 00:25:29,845
behind this.

393
00:25:30,814 --> 00:25:33,484
I'm certain,
but there's no evidence.

394
00:25:34,945 --> 00:25:37,385
That's not all, Gwang Jae.

395
00:26:12,254 --> 00:26:13,355
Hello?

396
00:26:14,254 --> 00:26:15,685
It's me, Lee Gwang Jae.

397
00:26:17,125 --> 00:26:20,324
The man dating Young Ha
in the night market.

398
00:26:22,425 --> 00:26:23,965
The jerk one.

399
00:26:25,435 --> 00:26:27,334
Oh, Gwang Jae. Yes.

400
00:26:29,234 --> 00:26:30,705
Can you meet me for a second?

401
00:26:32,175 --> 00:26:33,274
Come up.

402
00:26:45,814 --> 00:26:46,925
