about 5 million dollars.

414
00:27:38,474 --> 00:27:39,645
I want to get them back,

415
00:27:41,504 --> 00:27:43,215
and pay off my dad's debt.

416
00:27:46,415 --> 00:27:50,355
My heart is about to burst
due to resentment.

417
00:27:51,784 --> 00:27:52,984
I'm going to...

418
00:27:53,984 --> 00:27:55,385
get my house back.

419
00:27:56,024 --> 00:27:57,824
I'm going to get all that back.

420
00:27:58,425 --> 00:28:00,294
I'm not trying to keep it.

421
00:28:03,135 --> 00:28:06,504
I want to get it back,
so that I can pay off...

422
00:28:06,504 --> 00:28:08,004
to those who suffered
because of my dad.

423
00:28:10,205 --> 00:28:13,274
Please help me.

424
00:28:58,355 --> 00:29:01,324
(The Rich Son)

425
00:29:01,524 --> 00:29:04,125
We're not family anymore.
You're not my brother anymore.

426
00:29:04,125 --> 00:29:06,395
Don't be a coward, Director Nam!

427
00:29:06,395 --> 00:29:08,595
